    "John H. Walton, John K. Riches": "the Lord will deliver you into my hands\ufffd While Goliath\u2019s focus\nis his personal honor and prowess (vv. 43\u201344), David `[char_David_Rut_4]` focuses\nattention upon the Lord. David `[char_David_Rut_4]` will act to bring glory to God, not to\nhimself."
